      <title>根据连接的 wifi 自动切换 /etc/hosts</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/articles/%E6%A0%B9%E6%8D%AE%E8%BF%9E%E6%8E%A5%E7%9A%84-wifi-%E8%87%AA%E5%8A%A8%E5%88%87%E6%8D%A2-etc-hosts/</link>
